				<span class="hero-title-highlight">Reimagined</span>
			</h1>

			<p class="hero-description">
				Experience the next evolution of enterprise web development.
				Built on the bleeding edge of .NET 10, combining extreme performance with
				robust Clean Architecture principles.
			</p>

			<div class="d-flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap mt-8">
				<MudButton Href="https://architecture.blazorserver.com"
						   Variant="Variant.Filled"
						   Color="Color.Primary"
						   Size="Size.Large"
						   Class="btn-glow py-3 px-8 rounded-pill"
						   StartIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.RocketLaunch">
					Launch Demo
				</MudButton>
				<MudButton Href="https://github.com/neozhu/CleanArchitectureWithBlazorServer"
						   Target="_blank"
						   Variant="Variant.Outlined"
						   Size="Size.Large"
						   Class="btn-outline-tech py-3 px-8 rounded-pill"
						   StartIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Code">
